params._limitprice: trade price's limit~交易价格限制
params._referal: is need trade all~是否允许全部成交

params._limitprice: trade price's limit~交易价格限制
params._swapQuantity: buy good2's quantity~购买商品2的数量

returns.goodid1FeeQuantity_: good1 actual fee~商品1实际手续费

params._initial: initial good.amount0:normalgood quantity,amount1:valuegoodquantity~初始化的商品的参数,前128位为普通商品数量,后128位为价值商品数量.
params._valuegood: valuegood_no:measure the normal good value~价值商品编号:衡量普通商品价值

params._erc20address: good's contract address~商品合约地址
